2 Desert Large House (L-shaped house)
2.1 Materials
2.2 Blueprint

A common house made up of cobblestone, oak logs, oak planks, an oak door, glass panes, and oak stairs. This can be mirrored and the oak can be swapped out with spruce or acacia if it is the taiga or savanna variant, respectively.
About 83 Logs to have the 12 Logs, make the Oak Wood Stairs, and the Oak Wood Planks.
Build after the plans by User:Merdink

Note: the oak wood stairs are optional for the first layer and generates only if the house was spawned above street level.
Another Note: If the house was spawned level with the street, this floor has the cobblestone and planks in the ground instead of above the ground.
A common house made up of sandstone, smooth sandstone, a door, glass panes, and sandstone stairs.

Note: the sandstone stairs are optional for the first layer and generates only if the house was spawned above the street level.
Another Note: If the house was spawned level with the street, this floor has the sandstone in the ground instead of above the ground.
